{"tid":1885374,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"真攬炒: 多間酒店要求員工放無薪假 亦出現裁員","createTime":"2020-02-18T08:50:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T20:04:13.000Z","uid":292292,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"506a6ae506d6963fae1510f21f792a8acb61109f","tid":1885374,"uid":292292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T08:50:05.000Z","msg":"【多間酒店要求員工放無薪假 亦出現裁員】<a href=\"http://bit.ly/37D840z\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37D840z&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmhR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=f4e2c179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/37D840z</a><br />\n<br />\n酒店工會表示，在 #新冠病毒肺炎 疫情影響下，已經有17個集團旗下的多間酒店，要求員工放無薪假，亦有4間酒店裁員，形容情況令人憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n職工盟主席 #吳敏兒 指出，根據僱傭條例，接受檢疫又無確診的僱員，不符合領取疾病津貼資格，擔心僱員會因此逃避強制檢疫，影響防疫成效。要求政府修例，規定僱主支付疾病津貼予此類僱員，又促請政府將新型冠狀病毒列作職業病，方便染病僱員爭取工傷賠償。"},{"pid":"c9a4828c2d40d7455d0ce596e62885349577e15b","tid":1885374,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T08:50:48.000Z","msg":"恆指又升, 樓價又升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c923d0c5d711aa809351e929acda99c71bc6f4c6","tid":1885374,"uid":118120,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T08:51:19.000Z","msg":"有勇氣怪抗爭者搞壞個市<br />\n冇勇氣怪大陸搞個疫症出黎"},{"pid":"1c8589220cca909ea80676c0d1000d2f68d776af","tid":1885374,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T08:51:37.000Z","msg":"多謝林鄭"},{"pid":"36cad7e428c8fe74ce8bcab6c3765ad84595657b","tid":1885374,"uid":292292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c923d0c5d711aa809351e929acda99c71bc6f4c6","tid":1885374,"uid":118120,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T08:51:19.000Z","msg":"有勇氣怪抗爭者搞壞個市<br />\n冇勇氣怪大陸搞個疫症出黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T08:57:31.000Z","msg":"Why not both<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd985d4a0c241c3e30b7b74b62ca5ffd5105ce0f","tid":1885374,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0